      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "7df0ab20c2297aa2",
      "text": "(Q) In which epoch of hominid evolution would an adapted resonant mirror system enabling distant learning by virtual participation in the activity of adult models have afforded the most critical selective advantage? (Bråten 2002:274)"
